{"tid":1760524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無遇過d好硬頸既人","createTime":"2019-11-28T09:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T10:49:19.000Z","uid":194708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63eedf0108fbba9fbdf3fb81861fa77426b8893a","tid":1760524,"uid":194708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"即係佢明明想做，但俾你講左中，就即刻話邊有d咁既事<br />\n又例如佢明明鍾意黃色，俾你估中又話自己其實鍾意藍，結果就好唔憤氣，唯有隔一排等你唔記得先買返黃色野<br />\n<br />\n通常同呢d人講野，就唯有講相反既野迫佢做。<br />\n<br />\n話想我公司有個大佬，你明明想佢炒姓董果個，你又知佢想炒，點知有人一傳話炒佢，佢就即刻死攬，等你地班人覺得佢唔係咁易估。跟住隔左成年先話佢自己腳痛唔做。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩次又係咁，明明話炒姓林，再換埋個department head，一收到風d人就煲大，佢見事敗又要焗住死攬<br />\n<br />\n咁我老闆就好撚中意養d綠色昆蟲，我想問下如果下次傳老細死攬下屬，甚至不憎打架都要力保佢養果3萬隻昆蟲，佢會唔會嬲得滯一炮過dump哂佢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bf6de55335550985d38d47dc70f617752ea8fd","tid":1760524,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"姓林<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a238e80050ce705c8095a982b38cb7dfc85a147","tid":1760524,"uid":194708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bf6de55335550985d38d47dc70f617752ea8fd","tid":1760524,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"姓林<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"Sor hahahaha 公司d人叫佢林太"},{"pid":"86fa5a2401f749526f568f5c4a100e3140dc3b31","tid":1760524,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bf6de55335550985d38d47dc70f617752ea8fd","tid":1760524,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"姓林<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"呢個真，我都識一個"